---
// Experiencia section — vertical timeline with 4 professional experience items
---

<section id="experiencia" class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-12 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-20 flex flex-col gap-12">

    <!-- Section header: label + title only (no accent line) -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[1px] text-[var(--color-primary)]">EXPERIENCIA</span>
      <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-bold text-[var(--text-heading)]">Trayectoria Profesional</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Vertical timeline -->
    <div class="flex flex-col">

      <!-- Item 1: Tech Lead @ Real Plaza — filled dot + connecting line -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 pb-8 border-b border-[var(--border-default)] md:border-b-0">
        <!-- Left: date + company (hidden on mobile) -->
        <div class="w-[200px] flex-shrink-0 text-right hidden md:flex flex-col gap-1 pt-0.5">
          <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2022 — 2025</span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Real Plaza</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Center: dot + line -->
        <div class="w-6 hidden md:flex flex-col items-center flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary-bg)]"></div>
          <div class="w-[2px] bg-[var(--border-default)] flex-1"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: title + description — gap:8 per .pen -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2 pt-0.5">
          <!-- Inline date + company (mobile only) -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary-bg)] flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2022 — 2025</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Real Plaza</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-[var(--text-heading)]">Tech Lead</span>
          <p class="text-[14px] leading-[1.5] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            Lideré un equipo de 6 desarrolladores, logrando una reducción del 80% en bugs y un aumento del 40% en velocidad de entrega. Implementé arquitecturas basadas en microservicios y establecí estándares de calidad con 92% de cobertura de tests.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2: Technical Product Owner @ Real Plaza — hollow dot + connecting line -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 pb-8 border-b border-[var(--border-default)] md:border-b-0">
        <!-- Left: date + company (hidden on mobile) -->
        <div class="w-[200px] flex-shrink-0 text-right hidden md:flex flex-col gap-1 pt-0.5">
          <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2019 — 2022</span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Real Plaza</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Center: dot + line -->
        <div class="w-6 hidden md:flex flex-col items-center flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-[3px] border-[var(--color-primary)]"></div>
          <div class="w-[2px] bg-[var(--border-default)] flex-1"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: title + description — gap:8 per .pen -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2 pt-0.5">
          <!-- Inline date + company (mobile only) -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-2 border-[var(--color-primary)] flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2019 — 2022</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Real Plaza</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-[var(--text-heading)]">Technical Product Owner</span>
          <p class="text-[14px] leading-[1.5] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            Gestioné el backlog técnico y definí la visión de producto para plataformas digitales de comercio. Coordiné equipos cross-funcionales y mejoré procesos de entrega continua.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3: Analista Desarrollador @ Aceros Arequipa — hollow dot + connecting line -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 pb-8 border-b border-[var(--border-default)] md:border-b-0">
        <!-- Left: date + company (hidden on mobile) -->
        <div class="w-[200px] flex-shrink-0 text-right hidden md:flex flex-col gap-1 pt-0.5">
          <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2018</span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Aceros Arequipa</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Center: dot + line -->
        <div class="w-6 hidden md:flex flex-col items-center flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-[3px] border-[var(--color-primary)]"></div>
          <div class="w-[2px] bg-[var(--border-default)] flex-1"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: title + description — gap:8 per .pen -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2 pt-0.5">
          <!-- Inline date + company (mobile only) -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-2 border-[var(--color-primary)] flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2018</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Aceros Arequipa</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-[var(--text-heading)]">Analista Desarrollador</span>
          <p class="text-[14px] leading-[1.5] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            Desarrollé soluciones empresariales para procesos de manufactura y logística utilizando tecnologías .NET y SQL Server.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 4: Software Developer @ Divemotor — hollow dot, no line -->
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <!-- Left: date + company (hidden on mobile) -->
        <div class="w-[200px] flex-shrink-0 text-right hidden md:flex flex-col gap-1 pt-0.5">
          <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2017 — 2018</span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Divemotor</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Center: dot only, no line -->
        <div class="w-6 hidden md:flex flex-col items-center flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-[3px] border-[var(--color-primary)]"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: title + description — gap:8 per .pen -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-2 pt-0.5">
          <!-- Inline date + company (mobile only) -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-2 border-[var(--color-primary)] flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <span class="text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">2017 — 2018</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-[13px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Divemotor</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-[var(--text-heading)]">Software Developer</span>
          <p class="text-[14px] leading-[1.5] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            Desarrollé aplicaciones web y servicios backend para el sector automotriz, integrando sistemas ERP y plataformas de gestión comercial.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
